title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“I hope you can write six more volumes of your autobiography.” [Dick Cavett to former Prime Minister Macmillan, December 23, 1980. Submitted by Marion Nickel, Rhinebeck, New York.]
